  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Love racing games ? Don't like complex gameplay ? Have some time to waste ?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Turn on your old tv, connect your old console and just drive!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/a129d9867a3c8c220f1a60eb091cd1ac.poster.avif?t=1731240641\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/a129d9867a3c8c220f1a60eb091cd1ac.webm?t=1731240641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/a129d9867a3c8c220f1a60eb091cd1ac.mp4?t=1731240641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/8d7ba0a720e3fe04ae0964762db532ce.poster.avif?t=1731240641\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/8d7ba0a720e3fe04ae0964762db532ce.webm?t=1731240641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/8d7ba0a720e3fe04ae0964762db532ce.mp4?t=1731240641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You like creating 3D content and modding games ?</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create a track in your 3D software of choice, setup the track in Godot engine, export as a package, add it to the mods folder, enjoy your creation or share with friends and challenge them to beat your record</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Model your own car in your 3D software of choice or download one, setup the car in Godot engine, export as a package, add it to the mods folder, enjoy your creation or share it with friends</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Just a sweet time waster </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No complex gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play with a Keyboard or Gamepad </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 screen styles - Normal, Pixelated and CRT</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Drift mode </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time attack mode  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2 Players Split Screen </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No saves and loads </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > it's all about getting higher in leaderboards or just having fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 30+ unlocked cars   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play on custom made maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create and import your custom cars</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Love racing games ? Don't like complex gameplay ? Have some time to waste ?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Turn on your old tv, connect your old console and just drive!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/a129d9867a3c8c220f1a60eb091cd1ac.poster.avif?t=1731240641\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/a129d9867a3c8c220f1a60eb091cd1ac.webm?t=1731240641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/a129d9867a3c8c220f1a60eb091cd1ac.mp4?t=1731240641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/8d7ba0a720e3fe04ae0964762db532ce.poster.avif?t=1731240641\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/8d7ba0a720e3fe04ae0964762db532ce.webm?t=1731240641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746140/extras/8d7ba0a720e3fe04ae0964762db532ce.mp4?t=1731240641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You like creating 3D content and modding games ?</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create a track in your 3D software of choice, setup the track in Godot engine, export as a package, add it to the mods folder, enjoy your creation or share with friends and challenge them to beat your record</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Model your own car in your 3D software of choice or download one, setup the car in Godot engine, export as a package, add it to the mods folder, enjoy your creation or share it with friends</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Just a sweet time waster </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No complex gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play with a Keyboard or Gamepad </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 screen styles - Normal, Pixelated and CRT</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Drift mode </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time attack mode  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2 Players Split Screen </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No saves and loads </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > it's all about getting higher in leaderboards or just having fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 30+ unlocked cars   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play on custom made maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create and import your custom cars</p></li></ul>",
